---
---

<section class="story section" id="story">
  <div class="container story-inner">
    <!-- Photo side -->
    <div class="story-photo-wrap">
      <div class="story-photo">
        <img src="/cristian-pic.jpg" alt="Cristian Ungureanu, founder of Beehive Book Marketing" class="story-img" />
        <div class="story-photo-tint" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Floating founder card -->
      <div class="story-founder-card">
        <span class="story-founder-name">Cristian Ungureanu</span>
        <span class="story-founder-label">FOUNDER</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Decorative dots -->
      <div class="story-dots" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text side -->
    <div class="story-content">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Building in Public</span>
      <h2 class="story-heading">My Story</h2>

      <p class="story-body">
        Before starting Beehive, I spent <strong>8 years</strong> building growth engines in SaaS and
        hospitality — most recently at <strong>QuickMail.io</strong> and <strong>ScraperAPI.com</strong>,
        where the marketing systems I helped develop generated over <strong>$5 million in ARR</strong>.
        Funnels, attribution, conversion math — the SaaS playbook that actually compounds.
      </p>

      <p class="story-body">
        I started Beehive because the same playbook applies to books — positioning, audience, funnel,
        attribution, measurement. For an author whose book is meant to fill a pipeline, close
        deals faster, and unlock the keynote circuit, that's the work that compounds.
      </p>

      <p class="story-body">
        Right now, I'm writing, publishing, and marketing my own book using this exact process —
        in public, one cycle ahead of my first clients. Everything I sell, I'm doing myself first.
      </p>

      <!-- Stats row -->
      <div class="story-stats">
        <div class="story-stat">
          <span class="story-stat-number">$5M+</span>
          <span class="story-stat-label">ARR generated for tech clients</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="story-stat">
          <span class="story-stat-number">8+</span>
          <span class="story-stat-label">Years in growth marketing</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/about" class="story-link">
        Learn More About Me <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .story-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  /* Photo side */
  .story-photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }

  .story-photo {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .story-photo-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #E8A317 0%, #F4C557 50%, #D4920F 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .story-initials {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .story-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .story-photo-tint {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 50%,
      rgba(232, 163, 23, 0.15) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Founder card */
  .story-founder-card {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .story-founder-name {
    font-family: var(--font-script);
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .story-founder-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #E8A317;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Decorative dots */
  .story-dots {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px;
    right: -30px;
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #E8A317 1.5px, transparent 1.5px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
    opacity: 0.2;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  /* Content side */
  .section-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #E8A317;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .story-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-body {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #374151;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .story-body strong {
    color: #1A1A1A;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Stats */
  .story-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #FFF8E7;
    border-radius: 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,163,23,0.2);
  }

  .story-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .story-stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #E8A317;
  }

  .story-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .story-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 3rem;
    background: rgba(232,163,23,0.25);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* CTA link */
  .story-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #E8A317;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .story-link:hover {
    border-color: #E8A317;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .story-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .story-photo {
      max-width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
    }

    .story-initials {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
